  <Overview>Enterprise-grade messaging platform with AWS Pinpoint and SNS integration for 2-way SMS/MMS communication. Features contact management with import/export, conversation threading, keyword automation, real-time webhook processing, media attachments, RESTful API, and a modern React UI.</Overview>
  <Category>Network:Messaging Productivity: Tools: Status:Stable</Category>
  <WebUI>http://[IP]:[PORT:3000]</WebUI>
  <TemplateURL>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/N85UK/UNRAID_APP/main/templates/aws-ultimate-messaging.xml</TemplateURL>
  <Icon>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/N85UK/UNRAID_APP/main/icons/aws-ultimate-messaging.png</Icon>
